{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_lyjshzhwbn1l_1","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: About myBodyGraph — myBodyGraph\nURL: https://www.mybodygraph.com/about-us\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nmyBodyGraph is an official Human Design platform created by Jovian Archive. Founded by Ra Uru Hu in 1999, Jovian Archive has been managed by his family since his passing in 2011, ensuring the authentic transmission of his teachings.\n[...]\nDevelopment of myBodyGraph began in 2012, aiming to deliver accurate, accessible, and affordable Human Design analysis based directly on Ra’s extensive teachings. Over his 25-year teaching career, Ra produced more than 1,000 hours of recorded lectures, forming the foundation for our analytical tools and insights.\n[...]\nSince launching in 2014, myBodyGraph has provided the Human Design community with precise Foundational Analysis and powerful Transit Tools. By 2023, our platform celebrated one million registered accounts and underwent a comprehensive update—introducing an enhanced user experience, expanded features, and new offerings such as Partnership, Advanced, and Personal Success Analysis.\n[...]\nToday, Jovian Archive continues to oversee myBodyGraph alongside Maia Mechanics and the forthcoming Ra.tv, dedicated to the ongoing evolution and global growth of the Human Design system.\n[...]\nAntonio joined Jovian Archive in the mid 2000’s as technical support—online and live at Ra’s yearly Human Design events in Ibiza. He created Jovian Mobile in 2010, and began co-developing the 1st edition of myBodyGraph in 2012. Today, Antonio’s experience and steadfast reliability are employed on multiple projects.\n[...]\nA free account includes access to unlimited chart creation (personal, connection, and transit charts), a feature-packed library (filters, tagging, and over 45,000 celebrity charts), teachings specifically tailored to every chart you create, an interactive BodyGraph, and an extensive knowledge base with introductory articles and Ra’s Human Design dictionary.\n\n---\n\nTitle: myBodyGraph | Official Site of Human Design\nURL: https://www.mybodygraph.com/\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nmyBodyGraph | Official Site of Human Design\n[...]\nOFFICIAL HUMAN DESIGN PLATFORM\n[...]\nto source teachings about\n[...]\npersonal and relationship\n[...]\nwith a free myBodyGraph account.\n[...]\nRa Uru Hu’s Human Design teachings offer\n[...]\nand purpose.\n[...]\nthe layers of external conditioning.\n[...]\nImagine having a map—a guide that provides clarity about your true nature and offers direction towards your purpose. This is Human Design, a revolutionary system that combines principles of Astrology, Kabbalah, Hindu-Brahman Chakra, and the I Ching, to create a unique \"Design\" that's as individual as your DNA.This intricate Human Design BodyGraph is a snapshot of your energetic blueprint—it captures your strengths, challenges, and potential unlike anything else.\n[...]\nMeet Ra Uru Hu\n[...]\nIn 1987, Ra Uru Hu experienced a mystical encounter that lasted eight days and nights during which he received a transmission of information; what is known today as the Human Design System.Ra devoted the rest of his life to developing and teaching Human Design, serving as a guide for countless individuals seeking to understand themselves and their place in the world. His teachings are more than theoretical; they are practical tools for self-discovery and personal transformation.\n[...]\nA Foundational Analysis provides you with free access to all the information you need to begin experimenting with Human Design. Learn about your Strategy & Authority, begin your deconditioning process, and realign with your true path and potential with guidance from the founder, Ra Uru Hu.\n[...]\nstrengths, challenges, and areas of potential growth\n[...]\n, Companions\n[...]\n, and Love\n[...]\nAnalysis grants you\n[...]\nto the deeper layers of\n[...]\napply your personalized Dietary Regimen\n[...]\nto see,\n[...]\nyour unique Awareness\n[...]\nIntuitive Transit\n[...]\noffer you the ability to see how the planetary imprint interacts with your chart. Create Transit Charts between 1800 and 2100, generate Live Just Now & Just Now Connection Charts with a single click, and browse the interactive Ephemeris for recent and upcoming changes\n[...]\nWatch the Human Design Weather, Ra’s “first teacher in Human Design.”\n[...]\nA free account includes access to unlimited chart creation (personal, connection, and transit charts), a feature-packed library (filters, tagging, and over 40,000 celebrity charts), teachings specifically tailored to every chart you create, an interactive BodyGraph, and an extensive knowledge base with introductory articles and Ra’s Human Design dictionary.\n\n---\n\nTitle: What to Know About Human Design\nURL: https://www.verywellmind.com/what-is-human-design-8729468\nPublished: 2024-12-04T19:03:16.000Z\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nWe utilize new-age modalities like astrology, the enneagram, Myers-Briggs, and tarot as lenses through which we observe ourselves more clearly. Their legitimacy lies not in their ability to provide us with clinical or absolute truth, but in how they encourage us to cultivate self-awareness on our own terms. And while technically pseudoscience, most people who use them just think they're fun and occasionally helpful.\n[...]\nthe human design movement\n[...]\nManifesting-Generators: a hybrid of Manifestor and Generator types, the Manifesting Generator is a \"jack of all trades\". These people share characteristics with Manifestors and Generators but tend to be focused on one more than the other. They are the ones with all the ideas who are frequently jumping between projects—but this behavior benefits them. While generally recognized as its own energy type, The Jovian Archive, the organization founded by the creator of Human Design, combines Manifestors and Manifesting Generators together in their materials.\n[...]\nWhen identifying your energy centers, human design revolves around the use of a bodygraph, a type of chart that maps these energy areas. The thinking goes that if one of your energy centers is open—meaning it is receiving directions from the outside world—as opposed to defined or closed, then you are going to be influenced that way. The initial chart process includes sharing your name, the time you were born, and where you were born.\n[...]\nThe Jovian Archive, which is the founder’s company, gives the example of an open-head center leading you to overthink. Human Design calls these outside influences conditioning, which leads to your “not self”. In essence, the methodology is arguing that, if you are in touch with your body and your mind in a particular way, then you are in control and not have to fear bad decision-making.\n[...]\nI think the drawback to human design, or any other personality\n[...]\nbelief system for that matter, is that it runs the risk of\n[...]\npeople. I caution folks\n[...]\nIn terms of studies that are being done, research into the dangers of pseudoscience is ongoing. In a 2017 essay published by EMBO Reports, Princeton’s dean of the college and a history professor, Michael D Gordin, argues that the very term itself poses issues.\n[...]\n“...pseudoscience is science's shadow. Specifically, it is the shadow of professional science, and just as a shadow cannot exist without the object casting it, so does every object necessarily cast shadows. During the past two hundred years, demarcating what stands as legitimate, mainstream science from its less reputable counterparts on the fringe has been a central mechanism of how various disciplines have developed.”\n\n---\n\nTitle: The Source of Human Design | Ra Uru Hu\nURL: https://jovianarchive.com/\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nAs the Home of Human Design—founded by Ra Uru Hu in 1999—Jovian Archive Empowers through Authentic Teachings and Innovative Platforms\n[...]\nAbout Jovian Archive\n[...]\nLearn about Jovian Archive, founded by Ra Uru Hu in 1999. Discover the history and mission behind the source for the Human Design System.\n[...]\nDiscover the story of Ra Uru Hu, the founder of the Human Design System. Learn about the origins of Human Design, his transformative revelation, and his enduring legacy as the official source of this revolutionary knowledge.\n[...]\nDiscover why Human Design, a revolutionary system of self-knowledge and decision-making, is the Science of Differentiation. Learn how neutrinos, the BodyGraph, and planetary imprinting reveal your unique design and guide you to live authentically.\n[...]\nHuman Design from myBodyGraph\n[...]\nWe also recommend creating a free account at myBodyGraph.com for an interactive way to explore your design.\n[...]\nAll of our materials come directly from Ra Uru Hu, the founder and original messenger of the Human Design System. Jovian Archive is the official site for his recorded teachings, licensed publications, and curated educational content—developed and maintained by Ra’s family since his passing in 2011.\n[...]\nFor chart exploration tools, visit our sister site myBodyGraph.com.\n[...]\n## The Official Sites\n[...]\nJovian Archive\n[...]\nRa’s complete library—from fundamentals to advanced insights. Everything Human Design, one place.\n[...]\nmyBodyGraph\n[...]\nInteractive Human Design analysis tailored to you. Understand yourself and your connections clearly.\n[...]\nMaia Mechanics\n[...]\nPro-level online Human Design software. Precise, powerful, always updated.\n[...]\nJovian Archive\n[...]\nRa’s complete library—from fundamentals to advanced insights. Everything Human Design, one place.\n[...]\nmyBodyGraph\n[...]\nInteractive Human Design analysis tailored to you. Understand yourself and your connections clearly.\n[...]\nMaia Mechanics\n[...]\nPro-level online Human Design software. Precise, powerful, always updated.\n\n---\