oups.\n\n---\n\nTitle: Human Design Reader Certification\nURL: https://www.humandesignrevolution.co/reader-certification\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nA Self-Paced Reader Certification Program Designed to Help You Gain Chart Mastery, Deliver Powerful Readings and Become a Standout Human Design Professional.\n[...]\n= $250\n[...]\nValue = $250\n[...]\nTotal Value of Advanced Tracks: $997 USD Included with your certification at no additional cost.\n[...]\n#### Access to Full Self-Paced Curriculum + Training Resources (value = $4000)\n[...]\n#### Live Reader Q&A + Chart Lab Sessions(value = $6000)\n[...]\n#### Access to HDR Student Community on Telegram(value = $2000)\n[...]\nYou’ll never be on this learning journey alone with lifetime access to HDR's Student Community on Telegram. Here you’ll be free to ask Krystle & your peers all of your questions, have open discussions around\n[...]\nHD, collaborate and share your wins with your new Human Design Soul Tribe!\n[...]\nJoin today and get instant access to the full self-paced curriculum, bonuses, and Advanced Reader Expansion Tracks — so you can start learning right away at your own rhythm. You’ll also be invited to our ongoing live support calls, where students connect, practice chart readings, and receive real-time mentorship from Krystle.\n[...]\n️ Ongoing Live\n[...]\nStudent Community on Telegram\n[...]\n#### 6-Month Payment Plan\n[...]\n## $450 USD\n[...]\n6 Monthly Payments\n[...]\n-in-\n[...]\n## $2500 USD\n[...]\nlevels of the IHDS Professional Analyst Program\n[...]\nYou can start anytime. The Human Design Reader Certification is fully self-paced and open for enrollment year-round. Once you join, you’ll get instant access to the entire curriculum, bonus Advanced Reader Tracks, and the private student community.\n[...]\nYes. Once you complete your two practice readings and the integration steps, you’ll be recognized as an HDR Certified Reader.\n[...]\nYes—and\n[...]\n. You’ll learn how\n[...]\nreadings, integrate insights into coaching conversations, and adapt what you share based on each client’s goals—whether they’re seeking clarity on life purpose, business, relationships, or personal growth.\n[...]\nJoin today and get instant access to the full self-paced curriculum, bonuses, and Advanced Reader Expansion Tracks — so you can start learning right away at your own rhythm. You’ll also be invited to our ongoing live support calls, where students connect, practice chart readings, and receive real-time mentorship from Krystle.\n[...]\nFull Self-Paced Reader Certification Curriculum\n[...]\nAdvanced Track: Connection Chart Analysis\n[...]\nAdvanced Track: The Variables Course\n[...]\nAdvanced Track: Cosmic Chart Dive Series\n[...]\nOngoing Live Reader Q&A + Chart Lab Sessions✔️ Access to the HDR Student Community on Telegram\n[...]\n#### 6-Month Payment Plan\n[...]\n## $450 USD\n[...]\n#### Pay-in-Full\n[...]\n## $2500 USD"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b1f43cf0-0b01-4fcb-be5a-abcfd9b49660","uuid":"35337831-1de9-4a31-95f0-da622189c1f7","timestamp":"2026-06-10T16:11:37.131Z","tool_use_result":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: Human Design Certification — The Authentic Professional Path | The Human Design System\nURL: https://humandesign.school/human-design-certification\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\n🌱Entry LevelHuman Design Reader & Guide CertificationGuide clients through their foundational Human Design experience. Type, Strategy, Authority, the nine Centers. The fastest path to professional certification.From $2,150 · 6–12 months →\n[...]\n🔬ProfessionalHuman Design Analyst CertificationThe complete professional credential. All 64 Gates, 384 Lines of the Rave I'Ching, Four Views, chart synthesis, relationship analysis, Incarnation Crosses. Four professional training levels.From $6,650 · 2–4 years →\n[...]\n📊Business & CareerHuman Design for Business & Career ConsultingApply Human Design mechanics to team dynamics, career alignment, organizational analysis, and executive decision-making. Ra Uru Hu's original business application of the system.Multiple pathways · Flexible timeline →\n[...]\n| Certification | Duration | Investment | What You Can Do |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| LYD Guide | 6–12 months | $2,150 | Guide foundational HD sessions (Type, Strategy, Authority, Centers) |\n| Coach Practitioner | 6–12 months | $2,347 | Integrate HD into professional coaching practice |\n| Ra-Direct Certificate | 10–24 months | $197/mo | Deep study of Ra's original recordings; foundational mastery |\n| Analyst Level 1–4 | 2–4 years | $6,650 total | Complete individual chart readings; professional practice |\n[...]\nThe intermediate bridge ($399 + $850). Required\n[...]\nFour professional training levels. All 64 Gates, 384 Lines, Connections, Cycles, Incarnation Crosses, Analyst Exam. $6,650 across 2–4 years.\n[...]\nHuman Design readings\n[...]\narnation Cross\n[...]\n- Business and team consulting: Apply Human Design mechanics to team composition, organizational dynamics, and career alignment for executives and founders\n[...]\n- Practitioner marketplace listing: List your services on the Human Design professionals directory — connecting with clients who seek certified practitioners in direct Ra Uru Hu lineage\n[...]\n-Direct Certificate Pathway is structured over 10–24 months.\n[...]\nFrom $2,150 for a Living Your Design Guide certificate to approximately $6,650 for full Analyst certification across all four professional levels. The Ra-Direct Certificate Pathway is $197/month. Use our Certification Cost Calculator to map your specific path and investment.\n[...]\nA Living Your Design Guide is certified to introduce others to\n[...]\nYes. Human Design mechanics apply directly to organizational dynamics, team composition, career alignment, and executive decision-making. Ra Uru Hu developed specific tools for the business application of the system. ICONIC's curriculum includes business applications within the professional analyst training track. See our Human Design for Business page for full details.\n\n---\n\nTitle: Professional Training Academy/Professional Analyst - IHDS\nURL: https://www.ihdschool.com/education-curriculum/professional-analyst\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: Ihds School\nHighlights:\nThe Professional Analyst Education is a comprehensive program that involves three General Education Courses as prerequisites, and four Professional Level Courses, to be taken over three and one-half years.\n[...]\nPre-Requisites: IA Human Design Foundation Reading by an IHDS Certified Professional Analyst , and the General Education Foundation Courses: Living Your Design, Rave\n[...]\nand Rave Cartography.\n[...]\nThe General Education Courses, Living Your Design, Rave ABC and Rave Cartography, are the prerequisites for taking any advanced education program in Human Design. These courses give the foundation you will need before you move into more advanced areas of study. These courses are open to anyone with an interest in Human Design, not just those who intend to follow the Professional Analyst track. It is recommended that the student take a reasonable break between courses to allow time to absorb, process and digest the information - and most importantly, to have an opportunity to experiment with their Strategy and Authority.\n[...]\nThe goal of PTL-I is to develop professional level analytical skills. In this year long, three-semester course, prospective analysts learn the detail level of Human Design, and how to synthesize the BodyGraph. Through monthly study programs, and written and digitally recorded oral homework projects, students learn to integrate this detail into their surface level analysis skills. They will also practice and learn to Keynote, and learn the art of synthesizing a Human Design chart. Oral repetition will be stressed throughout to solidify competence, aid memorization, and develop chart-reading skills. Total study time is a minimum of 200 hours over the year.\n[...]\nRegular Price: $1150.00 (per semester)\n[...]\nThis is Level II of the Professional Analyst Training. Completion of all 4 Levels is required for certification. PTL-II is a two-semester program and is an interactive workshop that delivers extensive new content and approach. In the first semester, students will learn to give Connection (relationship) readings and the basic keys in relationship analysis. Students will be required to submit an analysis to demonstrate their grasp of the material.\n[...]\nRegular Price: $750.00 (per semester)\n[...]\nRegular Price: $800.00\n[...]\nPTL-IV is the final level of the professional analyst training to become a certified Human Design Analyst. The goal of PTL-IV is to guide and mentor you as you prepare for submitting your final reading to the testing Board for certification. During the course of the semester, we will work together on honing your reading skills. We will look at the structure and organization of your individual client readings.\n[...]\nRegular Price: $800.00\n[...]\nDiscount Price: $\n\n---\n\nTitle: Training Courses — Professional Human Design Education | The Human Design System\nURL: https://humandesign.school/training\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nFrom your first chart to professional analyst certification — structured programs with live mentorship, direct Ra Uru Hu lineage, and lifetime platform access.\n[...]\n🌱 Foundational Living Your Design AwakeningThe official Human Design entry point. Charts, Centers, Aura Types, Strategy & Authority — self-paced with lifetime platform access. $350 Enroll\n[...]\n🎓 Professional Human Design Analyst Training — Level 1All 64 Gates, 384 Lines of the Rave I'Ching, Keynoting & Synthesis, Four Views, Chart Analysis. The first of four professional levels. $3,450 Enroll\n[...]\n⬡ Professional Analyst Training Level 2 — Cycles & ConnectionsRelationship Connections Certificate + Cycles Certificate. Advanced design mechanics for client work. $1,600 